snippet: Jo-Wilfried Tsonga said he was confident he could beat Andy Murray in the Wimbledon quarter-finals after he won his fourth-round match when fellow Frenchman Richard Gasquet retired with a back injury on Monday....
lead_paragraph: Jo-Wilfried Tsonga said he was confident he could beat Andy Murray in the Wimbledon quarter-finals after he won his fourth-round match when fellow Frenchman Richard Gasquet retired with a back injury on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Tsonga Confident He Can Beat Murray in Last Eight
headline.main: Tsonga Confident He Can Beat Murray in Last Eight
